=Generate strategic Silo topics that build comprehensive topical authority around this Pillar:

PILLAR CONTEXT:
Topic: {{ $json['Product / Pillars'] }}
Description: {{ $json['Pillar Description'] }}

EXCLUDED TOPICS (already created):
{{ $json['Mofu Topics'] }}

STRATEGIC REQUIREMENTS:
Create 5-10 semantically-tight Silo topics that:
