SILO CONTEXT:
Topic: {{ $json['Topic'] }}
Description: {{ $json['Content Description'] }}

EXCLUDED TOPICS (already created):
{{ $json['TOFU Topics'] }}

STRATEGIC REQUIREMENTS:
Create 5-10 highly-specific Sub-Silo topics that:
1. Answer long-tail search queries
2. Demonstrate niche expertise
3. Build comprehensive silo coverage
4. Capture specific use cases and edge cases

Output as clean JSON array:
[
  {
    "topic": "Sub-silo topic title",
    "description": "Specific focus and silo connection"
  }
]

=Topic: {{ $json.Topic }}
Description: {{ $json.Description }}
----
Generate 5-8 realistic keywords that real people would actually type into Google when searching for this topic. Focus on:
- How ordinary users naturally search (not technical jargon)
- Common phrases people use in everyday language
- Questions or problems people are trying to solve
- Simple, conversational search terms

Return your answer as a JSON object with a "keywords" array, nothing else.

Example:
{
  "keywords": ["keyword phrase 1", "keyword phrase 2", "keyword phrase 3"]
}

